title: How to access contracts as a trainer
text: To access your contracts as a trainer in FitX, go to the contracts and payments page and scroll down to the 'Contracts' section, where you can apply a search filter and access all your contracts and respective payments.

title: How to access your active contract as a client
text: To access your active contract as a FitX client, go to the contract page and scroll down to the 'Current Contract' section, where you can view all your contract information and more.

title: How to reactivate your profile
text: To reactivate your FitX profile, go to the login page and log in to your account as usual. Your profile will then be reactivated.

title: How to add a CREF to your trainer account
text: To add a CREF to your trainer account in FitX, go to your profile, add your CREF number and location in the trainer modification form, and confirm the changes.

title: How to make reviews and complaints anonymous
text: To make your reviews or complaints anonymous on FitX, go to your profile, enable the anonymous review or complaint boxes in the settings form, and confirm the changes.

title: How to cancel a contract as a client
text: To cancel your contract as a FitX client, go to the contract page and scroll to the bottom of the 'Current Contract' section. Remember that refunds may vary depending on a number of factors, so make sure you understand the refund amount.

title: How to cancel a contract as a trainer
text: To cancel a contract as a trainer on FitX, go to the client page, go to the 'Active Clients' section, and look for cancellation and refund. There you can check the refund amount and cancel the contract.

title: How to change a client's training as a trainer
text: To change a client's training as a trainer in FitX, access the client page, go to the 'Active Clients' section, change the training plan in the training form, and confirm the change.

title: How to change your account email
text: To change your FitX account email, access your profile, update your email, confirm the changes, and then confirm your identity.

title: How to change the language to English or Portuguese
text: To change the language to English or Portuguese in FitX, access your profile, enable or disable the English language checkbox in the settings form, and confirm the changes. You can also change the language using the floating button at the top of the screen.

title: How to change the theme to dark or light
text: To change the theme to dark or light in FitX, go to your profile, enable or disable the dark theme checkbox in the settings form, and confirm the changes. You can also change the theme using the floating button at the top of the screen.

title: What is the Coachy chatbot
text: The FitX Coachy chatbot is the app's assistant that answers questions about fitness, bodybuilding, health, and the app's functionality and features.

title: How to access contracts as a client
text: To access your contracts as a FitX client, go to the contract page and scroll down to the 'Your Contracts' section, where you can view all your contract information.

title: How to access training as a client
text: To access your training as a FitX client, go to the training page by clicking the workout icon in the navigation bar, where you can view your complete training plan sent by your trainer.

title: How to complaint a trainer as a client
text: To complaint a trainer as a client on FitX, go to the trainer's profile and scroll down to the complaints section, where you can complaint them by filling out the complaint form and see complaints from other users.

title: How to connect to Mercado Pago as a trainer
text: To connect to Mercado Pago as a trainer on FitX, access your profile, click the Mercado Pago connection button, and follow the instructions for creating an account, if necessary, and authorizing the connection.

title: How to contract a trainer as a client
text: To contract a trainer as a client on FitX, access the trainer's profile and scroll down to the payment plans section, where you can view the trainer's available plans and pay for one by clicking the icon in the upper right corner.

title: How to limit simultaneous active contracts as a trainer
text: To limit your simultaneous active contracts as a trainer on FitX, access your profile, change the number of simultaneous contracts to the desired number in the trainer modification form, and confirm the changes. Remember that this action will affect all attempts to contract you.

title: How to Create a New Account
text: To create a new FitX account, log out of your current account, go to the registration page, and fill out the form with your credentials. After that, follow the instructions to create a client or trainer profile.

title: How to create a payment plan as a trainer
text: To create a payment plan as a trainer in FitX, go to the contracts and payments page and click the add payment plan button. You will then be redirected to the payment plan creation page.

title: How to create a trainer account
text: To create a trainer account on FitX, go to the registration page, fill out the form, and click 'I want to sign up as a trainer'.

title: How to create a training plan as a trainer
text: To create a training plan as a trainer in FitX, go to the training plans page and click the plus button. You will be redirected to the training plan creation page.

title: How to customize a exercise as a trainer
text: To create or customize a exercise as a trainer in FitX, go to the training plan creation page, navigate to the exercise form, and combine exercise options, equipment, execution, pulleys, attachments, position, and more to create a specific exercise.

title: How to customize a training plan as a trainer
text: On the training plan creation page as a trainer in FitX, you can customize the days, exercises, and sets of your workout quickly and efficiently.

title: How to disable email notifications
text: To disable FitX email notifications, go to your profile, uncheck the email notification box in the settings form, and confirm the changes.

title: How to deactivate your profile
text: To deactivate your FitX profile, go to your profile, scroll to the bottom of the page, and click 'Deactivate Profile'.

title: How to delete an account
text: To delete your FitX account, go to your profile, scroll to the bottom of the page, and click 'Delete Account'. Remember that this action will erase all your data without any chance of recovery.

title: How to edit your profile
text: To edit your FitX profile, go to your personal profile page. There you can view and edit your personal data and settings.

title: How to confirm your identity by sending a code by email
text: To confirm your identity by email on FitX, check that the email displayed is the same as yours, access your email and look for the message with a code sent by FitX. Then, enter the code in the form within 2 minutes, or click 'Resend Code' and repeat the process.

title: How to Log Out
text: To log out of your FitX account, go to your profile, scroll to the bottom of the page, and click 'Log Out'.

title: How to manage payment plans as a trainer
text: To manage payment plans as a trainer in FitX, access the contracts and payments page. There you can view, edit, remove, and add payment plans.

title: How to manage training plans as a trainer
text: To manage training plans as a trainer in FitX, go to the training plans page. There you can view, edit, remove, and add training plans.

title: How to edit characteristics
text: To edit your characteristics in FitX as a client, access your personal profile page. There you can view and edit your physical characteristics for a more tailored delivery of the trainer's services.

title: How to edit trainer data
text: To edit your trainer data in FitX, go to your personal profile page. There you can view and edit your professional data, such as your CREF, professional description, and specialties.

title: How to pause and unpause hiring as a trainer
text: To pause or unpause your hiring as a trainer on FitX, go to your profile, scroll to the bottom of the page, and click 'Pause Hiring' to pause, or 'Unpause Hiring' to unpause. Remember that this action will affect all attempts to contract you.

title: How to pay for a trainer's plan as a client
text: To pay for a trainer's plan as a client on FitX, access the trainer's profile and click on the payment icon for a plan. After that, you will be redirected to the Mercado Pago payment page, where you can choose the payment method and confirm the transaction.

title: Payment Methods and Forms
text: FitX payment methods and forms are limited to those available on the Mercado Pago payment page. The available methods are: credit card and Mercado Pago credit. Payment can be made in installments in some cases, but this is controlled by Mercado Pago. Options such as PIX will soon be available.

title: How to access and modify your profile
text: To access or modify your FitX profile, click on your photo or name in the navigation bar to be redirected to your profile page, where you can edit your personal data and settings.

title: Where to ask questions about FitX
text: To ask questions about FitX, access the Coachy chatbot by clicking the bot icon in the navigation bar and sending it a message. If it can't answer, send a message to fitx.app.2025@gmail.com.

title: How to rate a trainer as a client
text: To rate a trainer as a client on FitX, go to their profile and scroll down to the reviews section. There, you can rate them by filling out the review form and giving them a rating from 1 to 5 stars, as well as see reviews from other users.

title: How to recover a forgotten password
text: To recover your FitX account password, go to the login page and click 'I forgot my password', then follow the password recovery procedures.

title: How to remove a complaint as a client
text: To remove a complaint as a client on FitX, go to the trainer's profile and scroll down to the reviews section, where you can view your complaint and remove it.

title: How to remove a review as a client
text: To remove a review as a client on FitX, go to the trainer's profile and scroll down to the reviews section, where you can view your review and remove it.

title: How to save trainers as a client
text: To save trainers as a client on FitX, go to the home page and scroll down to the 'Other Trainers' section, where you can save up to 10 trainer profiles by clicking the icon in the top left corner of their cards.

title: How to access saved trainers as a client
text: To access saved trainers as a FitX client, go to the saved trainers page by clicking the save icon in the navigation bar.

title: How to search for trainers as a client
text: To search for trainers as a client on FitX, go to the home page and scroll down to the 'Other Trainers' section, where you can apply various search filters and access trainer profiles.

title: How to share a trainer as a client
text: To share a trainer as a client on FitX, click the arrow icon on the trainer's card, or on their profile page next to their name.

title: How to manage clients as a trainer
text: To manage your clients as a trainer in FitX, access the clients page, where you'll find the 'Active Clients' section, where you can view and interact with your current clients. In the 'Client History' section, you can view all your past clients, along with additional information such as the amount paid and the number of contracts.

title: How to view complaints as a trainer
text: To view complaints as a trainer on FitX, access your profile and scroll down to the complaints section, where you can see complaints that FitX clients have made to you.

title: How to access a trainer's profile as a client
text: To access a trainer's profile as a client on FitX, go to the home page and scroll down to the 'Other Trainers' section, where you can access a trainer's profile by clicking the icon in the upper right corner of their card.

title: How to see reviews as a trainer
text: To see reviews as a trainer on FitX, go to your profile and scroll down to the reviews section, where you can see the reviews that FitX clients have given you.

title: Trainer unavailable for hiring
text: If a trainer is unavailable for hiring on FitX, you can save their profile and access it more easily on the saved trainers page.
